Subject: [PATCH v3 09/11] clk: imx: scu: Fix kfree() of static memory on setting driver_override
Date:   Sun, 27 Feb 2022 14:53:27 +0100
Message-Id: <20220227135329.145862-3-krzysztof.kozlowski@canonical.com>
